      "writtenOn": "2017-04-03T19:33:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It\u0027s hard for me to consider this CL on its own without understanding the eventual goal. My gut feeling is that implementing find_breaks without considering flakes and using only blamelists will not end up working well in practice. A design doc would probably be worthwhile.",
